Description: colorize printed text on ANSI terminals
 Rainbow is a ruby gem for colorizing printed text on ANSI terminals. It
 provides a string presenter object, which adds several methods to your
 strings for wrapping them in ANSI escape codes. These codes when printed in a
 terminal change text attributes like text color, background color, intensity
 etc.
